import React from 'react'

import Card from '../UI/Card'
import classes from './Order.module.css'
import OrderItem from './OrderItem'

const Order = (props) => {
  return (
    <section className={classes.orderMain}>
      <Card style={{ height: '100%' }}>
        <OrderItem />
      </Card>
    </section>
  )
}

export default Order
